text: མཚལ་མིན་པ་བསོད་ནམས་བཟང་པོའི་གསུང་འབུམ། Works of Tsalminpa Sonam Zangpo 擦蒙巴·頌囊菘博大師全集
zh-TW: 擦蒙巴·頌囊菘博大師全集
zh-CN: 擦蒙巴·颂囊菘博大师全集

nodes.en: Volume 1, ༼ཀ༽
rgyas pa'i bstan bcos tshad ma rnam 'grel gyi 'grel bshad rin chen phreng ba'i dkar chag
rgyas pa'i bstan bcos tshad ma rnam 'grel gyi 'grel bshad rin po che'i phreng ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so/ /
le'u gnyis pa'i rnam bshad gsal ba bzhugs so/ /lam dang lam min phye ste tshad ma mdo yi mchod brjod tshigs bcad bshad pa/
mngon sum le'u'i rnam bshad bzhugs so/ /log rtog rnam bzhi bsal te tshad ma mdo yi mngon sum le'u bshad pa/
le'u bzhi pa'i rnam bshad gsal bar bzhugs so/ /sgrub ngag don bcas bshad de tshad ma mdo yi gzhan don le'u bshad pa/
Volume 2, ༼ཁ༽
dkar chag
gtan tshigs rigs pa'i don bsdus pa rin po che'i phreng ba bzhugs so/ /
shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i lus rnam bzhag gi bsdus don rin chen phreng ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so/ /
dbu ma chos kyi dbyings su bstod pa'i rnam par bshad pa snying po gsal ba zhes bya ba bzhugs/
chos kyi dris lan legs bshad rgya mtsho bzhugs so/ /
chos 'byung rin po che'i gter zhes bya ba bzhugs/
'dul ba bdud rtsi'i nying khu zhes bya ba bzhugs/
'dul ba'i lag len rin po che'i gter bzhugs/
Volume 3, ༼ག༽
dkar chag
bla ma'i rnal 'byor byin rlabs kyi 'jug ngogs mdor bsdus zhes bya ba bzhugs so/ /
sbyor ba yan lag drug gi ring brgyud nye brgyud kyi gsol 'debs bzhugs so/ /
sbyor ba yan lag drug gi ngo sprod rab gsal zla ba bzhugs so/ /
sbyor ba yan lag drug gi khrid yig thog mtha' bar gsum bzhugs so/ /
dpal dus kyi 'khor lo'i yongs rdzogs kyi sgrub thabs dpag bsam gyi 'bras bu bzhugs/
dpal dus kyi 'khor lo'i dkyil 'khor du bdag nyid 'jug cing dbang bskur ba'i cho ga bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho bzhugs/
dpal dus kyi 'khor lo'i sgo nas gshin po rjes su 'dzin pa'i cho ga thar pa bgrod byed ces bya ba bzhugs so/ /
dpal dus kyi 'khor lo'i zhi rgyas kyi sbyin sreg gi cho ga ye shes kyi me rab tu gsal ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so/ /
dus 'khor lugs kyi rab tu gnas pa'i cho ga bkra shis rgya mtsho zhes bya ba bzhugs so/ /
rdo rje rnam 'joms mthing nag gi mngon rtogs khrus chog gzungs mdo dang bcas pa bzhugs so/ /
rdo rje rnam par 'joms pa zhes bya ba'i gzungs/
rgyal po chen po rnam thos sras mchod pa'i cho ga rin po che'i gter zhes bya ba bzhugs/
sangs rgyas kyi dus chen bzhi dang brgyad kyi ngos 'dzin snyag phu pas mdzad pa'o/ /
snyan ngag gi bstan bcos dge legs kun 'byung bzhugs/
gsang tshig snying gi gtam/
zlos gar gyi bstan bcos zab yangs gsal ba zhes bya bzhugs so//
bya bral ba bsod nams bzang pos sbyar ba/
dmar khrid gsol 'debs bzhugs so//
rje btsun bsam gtan gling pa nam mkha' bsod nams kyi bstod pa 'phags pa'i dbyangs zhes bya ba bzhugs/
sprang ban bsod nams bzang po rang gi spyod tshul dang bstun te/ bla ma la gsol ba 'debs pa/
ra pa mdo pa rin chen dpal bzang po la gnang ba'i bka' shog bzhugs/
rje bsam gtan gling pa nam mkha' bsod nams kyi bstod pa bzhugs so//
rje bsam gtan gling pa nam mkha' bsod nams kyi bstod pa'o//
lcang lung rin po che gzhon nu blo gros kyi bstod pa zla ba'i phreng ba/
chen po dpal 'byor rgya mtsho'i bstod pa gzhung bzang gangs ri ma smon lam dang bcas pa bzhugs so/ /
grub rgyal lugs kyi tshe dpag med kyi bstod pa zla ba'i 'od zer/
slob dpon padma 'byung gnas kyi bstod pa bzhugs so/ /
dbyangs can ma'i bstod pa/
ni gu brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs/
mkha' spyod chos rdzong gi gnas bstod rang la bskul pa'i gtam dang bcas pa'o//
tshigs su bcad pa utpa la sngon po'i phreng ba'o//
phyis 'byung gi dam pa rnams la gtam du che ba'i phreng ba'o//
tshigs su bcad pa rab dkar phreng 'dzin bzhugs/
rgyal khams pas yi ger bkod pa/
chen po dpal 'byor ba la phul ba'i zhu yig
ka mad sum cu'i sgo nas tshigs su bcad pa/
dbon po lha dbang rin chen la gdams pa/
lam 'bras brgyud pa'i gsol 'debs bzhugs/
rje sems dpa' chen po'i rnam thar la yi rang ba'i tshigs bcad bzhugs/
sgrol ma dkar mo la rgya gzhung dang mthun par bstod pa bzhugs/
a ti'i nyams len ka mad sum cu dang sbyar ba bzhugs/
seng ge sgang du brgyad stong pa bzhengs pa'i dkar chag dge legs kun 'byung bzhugs/
rje bsam gtan gling pa'i man ngag phra men ma'i bsgom bzlas bstod pa dang bcas pa bzhugs/
Volume 4, ༼ང༽
dkar chag
bde mchog mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho'i dbang chog dbang gi rgyal po'i rgyan ces bya ba bzhugs so/ /
mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho'i sbyin sreg gi cho ga ye shes kyi me 'od 'bar ba zhes bya bzhugs so//
dpal gshin rje gshed dmar lha lnga'i sgrub thabs rab gsal snang ba'i rgyan bzhugs/
padma dbang chen yang gsang khros pa'i dbang chog padma'i rigs kyi snying po bzhugs so/ /
phag mo shes rab gsal byed ma'i byin rlabs kyi cho ga bzhugs/
na ro mkha' spyod kyi sgrub thabs dang dbang chog bzhugs/
bcom ldan 'das kun rig gi cho ga snyag dbon rin po ches bsgrigs pa lho sgo cho ga dang bcas pa bzhugs so/ /
bkra shis tshigs su bcad pa/
phyag rgya bzhi'i rgyas gdab bzhugs so/ /
sman bla'i mchod phreng bzhugs so/ /
'phags pa gnas brtan bcu drug la gsol ba gdab pa'i cho ga bklags pa tsam gyis don 'grub pa bzhugs so/ /
bcu gcig zhal gyi bla ma brgyud par bcas pa'i rnam par thar pa bzhugs so//
bsnyung bar gnas pa'i cho ga de nyid bcu drug dge slong ma dpal mo'i lugs jo gdan bsod nams bzang po'i mdzad pa bzhugs so/ /
thugs rje chen po zhal bcu gcig pa'i sgrub pa dang bsnyung ba'i cho ga zhes bya ba bzhugs so/ /
bsnyung gnas kyi chos skor dang thugs rje chen po zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa'i sgom bzlas bzhugs so/ /
spyan ras gzigs phyag stong spyan stong dang ldan pa'i dbang gi cho ga thugs rje'i 'byung gnas zhes bya ba bzhugs so/ /
'phags pa don yod zhags pa lha lnga'i gzungs kyi bsgrub pa'i cho ga bzhugs so/ /
bcu gcig zhal gyi sbyin sreg
